*konsole-3.5.2-r1 (17 Apr 2006)

  17 Apr 2006; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org>
  +files/konsole-3.5.2-session-save-crash.fix.diff,
  +konsole-3.5.2-r1.ebuild:
  Fix session code related crashes.

  06 Apr 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> -konsole-3.5.0.ebuild,
  -konsole-3.5.1.ebuild, -konsole-3.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  Removed old 3.5.0/3.5.1 packages.

  01 Apr 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> konsole-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Add ~x86-fbsd keyword.

  28 Mar 2006; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> konsole-3.5.0.ebuild,
  konsole-3.5.1.ebuild, konsole-3.5.1-r1.ebuild, konsole-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Mark 3.5.2 3.5.1-r1 3.5.1 3.5.0 ~ia64

  27 Mar 2006; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> konsole-3.4.3.ebuild:
  Mark 3.4.3 stable on ia64. #112842

*konsole-3.5.2 (22 Mar 2006)

  22 Mar 2006; Dan Armak <danarmak@gentoo.org> +konsole-3.5.2.ebuild:
  KDE 3.5.2. Not yet released upstream, and so package.masked for now.

  09 Mar 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  konsole-3.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  Add dependencies for modular x, see bug #125562.

*konsole-3.5.1-r1 (24 Feb 2006)

  24 Feb 2006; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  +files/konsole-3.5.1-detach-send2all.patch, +konsole-3.5.1-r1.ebuild:
  When detaching a session, drop the connection if 'Send Input to All' is
  enabled, see KDE bug #119245. Thanks to Malcolm Lashley <malc@gentoo.org>
  for reporting.

